Contact and Maintenance Information¶

Questions and support¶

Questions can be mailed to WebLion support (support@weblion.psu.edu) or asked in the #weblion IRC channel on the Freenode network.

Report a bug¶

Submit bugs to WebLion support (support@weblion.psu.edu).
